text: Pierre Plihon is an archer from France. He was born on 29 October 1989. Plihon competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Pierre PlihonPierre PLIHON == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:French archers Category:Olympians for France Category:Sportspeople from Nice
